This is our 200th post! It didn't take even close to 200 days after meeting Geraldine to know that she is the love of my life. I waited till we reached this iconic place to propose, a stunning symbol of love. On 5th December 2019, I finally did it. And she said YES ! It was the best backdrop for this beautiful moment 🥂❤
